name: cute cupcake charm
description:
cute handmade cupcake charm made using polymer clay.
size is approx: 1cm X 1cm 

great to attach onto necklaces, bracelets, earrings or anything else you can think of...

all the charms come with a lobster clasp attached to them to make it easier for you to use and clip onto whatever you want !!

other "flavours" are available so please let me know if you have any preferences so i can organise a custom order for you !
contact me at : aef.3@hotmail.co.uk

note: the price shown is the cost of ONE charm

THANK YOU FOR LOOKING :)
